Repeat: sl 1 wyib, k1, sl 1 wyib, k3
sl 3 wyib, k1, insert needle under the loose Color b strand on front of work and knit the next stitch, catching strand behind stitch; k1
sl 1 wyib, k1, sl 1 wyib, k3
insert needle under the loose Color b strand on front of work and knit the next stitch, catching strand behind stitch; k1, sl 3 wyib, k1
End Row: insert needle under the loose Color b strand on front of work and knit the next stitch, catching strand behind stitch; k2
